@author         Seishiin
@description    `A dark and sleek theme for googleSupports:<ul><b>  <li>Search</li>  <li>Translator</li>  <li>Calendar</li>  <li>Drive</li>  <li>Docs</li>  <li>Photos</li>  <li>Scholar</li>  <li>Books</li>  <li>Shopping</li>  <li>News</li>  <li>Keep</li>  <li>Play</li></ul></b><b>Note:</b> Gmail has a built-in dark themeFound a bug? Tell me in the comment section below! But be specific and provide a screenshot if you can.After the bug you have submitted has been fixed, please consider changing your rating to a positive one. Thanks.`
@version        20190207.21.41
@license        CC-BY-NC-4.0
@preprocessor   uso
==/UserStyle== */
