@author         Lillies
@description    `This is a modified theme built off of <a href= "https://userstyles.org/users/498732">pyro1g</a>'s <a href="https://userstyles.org/styles/147594/canvas-instructure-dark-mode-bcps">Canvas/Instructure Dark Mode (BCPS)</a> themeThis is originally and still meant for personal usage between school + home devices. Updated as long as I'm in school`
@version        20181210.2.14
@license        NO-REDISTRIBUTION
@preprocessor   uso
==/UserStyle== */
